data: {"created":"2026-03-11T17:00:11.790075196Z","hasMore":true,"id":"msg_01CNA4kf35xpBNP5grhp3PGB","items":[{"hasMore":false,"id":"msg_01CNA4kf35xpBNP5grhp3PGB-0","partial":true,"text":"Good, I have both tools ready. Now let me run all 5 searches in parallel.","type":"text"},{"arguments":"{\"command\": \"cd /home/nanobot/sessions/2120ea74-b7f3-4eb4-abfe-145b7ad213d5 \u0026\u0026 MCP_CONFIG_PATH=.nanobot/mcp_servers.json mcp-cli call duckduckgo search '{\\\"query\\\": \\\"US-China trade war tariffs latest news 2025\\\", \\\"max_results\\\": 10}'\", \"timeout\": 60000, \"description\": \"Search 1: latest news 2025\"}","callID":"toolu_01RD1Zx8aTKUxBVKmKA3VarW","id":"msg_01CNA4kf35xpBNP5grhp3PGB-1","name":"bash","output":{"content":[{"text":"Found 10 search results:\n\n1. US-China Tariff Rates - What Are They Now?\n   URL: https://www.china-briefing.com/news/us-china-tariff-rates-2025\n   Summary: A summary ofUS-Chinatariffrates in effect in2025, including majortradeactions and how differenttariffsintersect.\n\n2. Trump's Trade War With China Catches the World in Its Crossfire\n   URL: https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/14/business/economy/us-china-trade-tariffs-global-economy.html\n   Summary: Thetradeclash between the world's two largest economies is rippling worldwide â ships made inChinafaceU.S.tariffswhen docking at American ports. Credit...Scott McIntyre for TheNewYork ...\n\n3. China won the 2025 battle in Trump's trade war. Here's what ... - CNBC\n   URL: https://www.cnbc.com/2025/12/31/trump-china-trade-war-tariffs.html\n   Summary: Chinaended the year of President Trump's aggressivetariffspolicy with a trillion-dollartradesurplus. That's an economic and political win for now.\n\n4. Tariff ruling stirs new uncertainty for US-China trade ties | AP News\n   URL: https://apnews.com/article/tariffs-china-trump-trade-supreme-court-fb8d38ae3664e845199d13113d03b471\n   Summary: WASHINGTON (AP) â The Supreme Court decision striking down President Donald Trump's swee