data: {"created":"2026-03-11T17:02:28.587932883Z","hasMore":true,"id":"09c23644-3a5c-4d4c-a910-cfc1526bebf5","items":[{"hasMore":false,"id":"09c23644-3a5c-4d4c-a910-cfc1526bebf5_0","partial":false,"text":"PHASE 2 â CHART CONFIGURATION\n\nNow, describe exactly how you would configure the AntV generate_dual_axes_chart call using this dataset:\n\n- X-axis â month\n- Left Y-axis â revenue (Column chart)\n- Right Y-axis â profit_margin (Line chart)\n- Chart title â \"Revenue vs Profit Margin â 2025 Trend Analysis\"\n- Enable tooltip\n- Enable legend\n- Smooth line â true\n- Responsive â true\n- Show grid lines\n\nFormatting:\n- Format revenue as currency ($)\n- Format profit_margin as %\n- Show data labels on line series\n- Use distinct colors for column and line\n\nDo NOT invent a different dataset. Focus on explaining the configuration and formatting in a way that could be passed to AntV or another charting library.","type":"text"}],"role":"user"}

data: {"created":"2026-03-11T17:02:30.297474649Z","hasMore":true,"id":"msg_018BnAFPHA4x49kigWGMqPoh","items":[{"hasMore":true,"id":"msg_018BnAFPHA4x49kigWGMqPoh-0","partial":true,"text":"\n\n## Phase 2 â Chart Configuration Plan\n\nHere is the exact configuration I will pass to `generate_dual_axes_chart` on the AntV Charts MCP server.\n\n---\n\n### Data Structure\n\nThe dataset remains unchanged â 12 records, each with `month`, `revenue`, and `profit_margin`.\n\n### Axis Mapping\n\n| Axis | Field | Chart Type | Y-Axis Position |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| X-axis | `month` | Shared | Bottom |\n| Left Y-axis | `revenue` | **Column** (bar) | Left |\n| Right Y-axis | `profit_margin` | **Line** | Right |\n\n### Configuration Breakdown\n\n**1. Core Layout**\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|","type":"text"}],"role":"assistant"}

