data: {"created":"2026-03-11T17:02:33.966825936Z","hasMore":true,"id":"msg_018BnAFPHA4x49kigWGMqPoh","items":[{"hasMore":false,"id":"msg_018BnAFPHA4x49kigWGMqPoh-0","partial":true,"text":"---|\n| `title` | `\"Revenue vs Profit Margin â 2025 Trend Analysis\"` |\n| `xField` | `\"month\"` |\n| Responsive | `true` â chart adapts to container width |\n\n**2. Left Y-Axis â Revenue (Column)**\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `yField` | `\"revenue\"` |\n| Geometry | `column` |\n| Color | A distinct brand color (e.g., `#5B8FF9` â blue) |\n| Axis label format | Currency: `$120,000` style (`$` prefix + comma separator) |\n| Grid lines | Enabled |\n\n**3. Right Y-Axis â Profit Margin (Line)**\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `yField` | `\"profit_margin\"` |\n| Geometry | `line` |\n| Color | A contrasting color (e.g., `#5AD8A6` â green) |\n| Smooth | `true` â curved interpolation between points |\n| Axis label format | Percentage: `18%` style (numeric value + `%` suffix) |\n| Data labels | Enabled on each point, formatted as `XX%` |\n| Point markers | Enabled for clarity |\n\n**4. Interactive Features**\n\n| Feature | Setting |\n|---|---|\n| Tooltip | Enabled â shows both revenue (formatted as `$XXX,XXX`) and profit margin (formatted as `XX%`) on hover |\n| Legend | Enabled â displays \"Revenue\" and \"Profit Margin\" with color swatches |\n\n**5. Visual / Grid**\n\n| Property | Value |\n|---|---|\n| Grid lines (left axis) | Visible, light gray, dashed |\n| Grid lines (right axis) | Hidden (to avoid visual clutter with two grids) |\n| Column corner radius | Slight rounding for a modern look |\n\n---\n\n### Equivalent JSON Config (AntV-style)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"title\": \"Revenue vs Profit Margin â 2025 Trend Analysis\",\n  \"xField\": \"month\",\n  \"data\": [\n    { \"month\": \"Jan\", \"revenue\": 120000, \"profit_margin\": 18 },\n    { \"month\": \"Feb\", \"revenue\": 135000, \"profit_margin\": 20 },\n    { \"month\": \"Mar\", \"revenue\": 150000, \"profit_margin\": 19 },\n    { \"month\": \"Apr\", \"revenue\": 165000, \"profit_margin\": 22 },\n    { \"month\": \"May\", \"revenue\": 190000, \"profit_margin\": 24 },\n    { \"month\": \"Jun\", \"revenue\": 210000, \"profit_margin\": 26 },\n    { \"month\": \"Jul\", \"revenue\": 230000, \"profit_margin\": 25 },\n    { \"month\": \"Aug\", \"revenue\": 250000, \"profit_margin\": 28 },\n    { \"month\": \"Sep\", \"revenue\": 240000, \"profit_margin\": 27 },\n    { \"month\": \"Oct\", \"revenue\": 270000, \"profit_margin\": 30 },\n    { \"month\": \"Nov\", \"revenue\": 300000, \"profit_margin\": 32 },\n    { \"month\": \"Dec\", \"revenue\": 340000, \"profit_margin\": 35 }\n  ],\n  \"children\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"interval\",\n      \"yField\": \"revenue\",\n      \"color\": \"#5B8FF9\",\n      \"label\": false,\n      \"axis\": {\n        \"y\": {\n          \"position\": \"left\",\n          \"title\": \"Revenue ($)\",\n          \"labelFormatter\": \"$,.0f\",\n          \"grid\": true\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"type\": \"line\",\n      \"yField\": \"profit_margin\",\n      \"color\": \"#5AD8A6\",\n      \"smooth\": true,\n      \"point\": true,\n      \"label\": {\n        \"formatter\": \"{value}%\"\n      },\n      \"axis\": {\n        \"y\": {\n          \"position\": \"right\",\n          \"title\": \"Profit Margin (%)\",\n          \"labelFormatter\": \".0f%\",\n          \"grid\": false\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"tooltip\": true,\n  \"legend\": true,\n  \"responsive\": true\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\n- **Two geometries** on one shared x-axis: blue columns for revenue, green smooth line for margin.\n- **Formatting** ensures revenue reads as dollars and margin reads as percentages â both in axis labels and tooltips.\n- **Data labels** appear only on the line series to avoid clutter on the columns.\n- **Grid lines** are shown only for the left (revenue) axis.\n\nConfiguration is locked in. Ready to execute the actual `generate_dual_axes_chart` call in **Phase 3** on your signal.","type":"text"}],"role":"assistant"}

