data: {"created":"2026-03-11T17:39:01.054367995Z","hasMore":true,"id":"msg_01RwQYWZxoZfUgCxSd9tYufJ","items":[{"hasMore":true,"id":"msg_01RwQYWZxoZfUgCxSd9tYufJ-0","partial":true,"text":"## Phase 3 â Visual Analysis\n\n---\n\n### 1. Five Key Insights from the Trend\n\n| # | Insight |\n|---|---|\n| 1 | **Sustained revenue growth:** Revenue nearly tripled from $120K (Jan) to $340K (Dec), representing a 183% year-over-year increase within the calendar year. |\n| 2 | **Accelerating profit efficiency:** Profit margin expanded from 18% to 35%, meaning the business is not just growing top-line but converting a larger share of revenue into profit over time. |\n| 3 | **Strongest growth corridor in H2:** The Jul-Dec period added $110K in monthly revenue ($230K to $340K) compared to $110K across the entire H1 ($120K to $230K), but H2 did it with consistently higher margins (25-35% vs 18-26%). |\n| 4 | **Q4 dominance:** Oct-Dec accounts for $910K in revenue (roughly 35% of the $2.6M annual total) with the three highest margin months of the year. |\n| 5 | **Minor dips are temporary:** Both the Sep revenue dip and the Mar/Jul margin dips recovered within one month, indicating","type":"text"}],"role":"assistant"}

